### Threads Integration Test Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Connect Threads Account (Step 1 - Get OAuth URL)
POST {{baseUrl}}/services/threads/connect
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "YOUR_BRAND_ID"
}

### Verify Threads OAuth (Step 2 - After redirect)
POST {{baseUrl}}/services/threads/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "AUTH_CODE_FROM_REDIRECT",
  "state": "{\"organizationId\":\"ORG_ID\",\"userId\":\"USER_ID\",\"brandId\":\"BRAND_ID\"}"
}

### Get Threads Trends
GET {{baseUrl}}/services/threads/trends
Authorization: {{token}}
